{"tid":726432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[袁志偉復仇戰]林鄭月娥上任一周年 財政措施成效大檢閱","createTime":"2018-07-02T11:32:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T11:11:09.000Z","uid":20816,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0fe8899fba82d25336182c012543fd76bb55547e","tid":726432,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:32:59.000Z","msg":"過去一年政府開支預算破紀錄，行政長官林鄭月娥提出「理財新哲學」，她的財政措施是否用得其所？  <br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥上任後，本年度公共開支預算增至近5,600億元，破了回歸以來紀錄，經常性開支較上年度多一成。  <br />\n<br />\n政府過往少有大筆投資的創新科技，本年度一口氣撥500億元，其中200億元建設河套區。有業界指除了錢，仍有其他問題要解決。  <br />\n<br />\n香港資訊科技聯會前會長黃錦輝表示：「搞創科這樣東西是多多益善，好多傳統法例未必適用，如何做一些新法例出來，令我們可促進新的科技的商業化，這是急需要做的問題。」  <br />\n<br />\n教育、社福、經濟方面的開支增幅均超過兩成，有民主派議員指，復康服務的確多了錢用，但院舍興建及居家安老方面，人手同規劃未能做好配合。  <br />\n<br />\n工黨新界東議員張超雄表示：「部門之間的協調，劃地的時候，包括私樓或公共設施的地，如果不放這些規劃下去，我們空有金錢，都沒有設施提供。」  <br />\n<br />\n花得多，賺得更多，就可以補回，但今年經濟增長預測只得百分之3至4%，經常性開支增長是11.8%，庫房其中主要收入來源，是難以預測的賣地收入及印花稅。  <br />\n<br />\n浸大財務及決策系副教授麥萃才認為，財政儲備豐厚，用來增加經常性開支合適，而支持教育、創科是投資未來，但短期內未必見到成效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5b3a0255e603835d6e0f02b9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5b3a0255e603835d6e0f02b9%2F&d=nbPBpL95CC5kiLBe3I2%2FdzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=f7dc8bdf\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5b3a0255e603835d6e0f02b9/</a>"},{"pid":"b53484f302eaff816133ce379f36d9577ba8872a","tid":726432,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"仲有<br />\n<br />\n政府擬周四公布終身年金詳情 學者提醒非與通脹掛勾　<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5b3a0274e6038386490f02b3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5b3a0274e6038386490f02b3%2F&d=nbPBpL95CC5kiLBe3I2%2FdzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=f80ed532\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5b3a0274e6038386490f02b3/</a>"},{"pid":"f567238ced6050217430f4917308717ff39a4c9b","tid":726432,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209f1180093aefe3d2d946ff24750586a051b97b","tid":726432,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:50:32.000Z","msg":"睇錯曾智偉"},{"pid":"bf3da54f329e36729800ce7eb5cd6bd739cb9cde","tid":726432,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"209f1180093aefe3d2d946ff24750586a051b97b","tid":726432,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:50:32.000Z","msg":"睇錯曾智偉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33bb114f4a7ac1890dc94a74dcbf0fd6fc6b08aa","tid":726432,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:53:44.000Z","msg":"咁袁花以後仲奶唔奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a434f1771e5bccd61562058cb3a275ab73733700","tid":726432,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"33bb114f4a7ac1890dc94a74dcbf0fd6fc6b08aa","tid":726432,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:53:44.000Z","msg":"咁袁花以後仲奶唔奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:55:27.000Z","msg":"希望日日狙擊林鄭"},{"pid":"3d372f6d97f47a3c7a89f446b89604388ae11266","tid":726432,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T13:50:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361c4d5d882029889666f05b2f6c0755eeac3e5f","tid":726432,"uid":54516,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"33bb114f4a7ac1890dc94a74dcbf0fd6fc6b08aa"